{"tid":2407894,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"迎接情人節！三上悠亞曝甜點塔　美胸巧妙溢出…網失焦了","createTime":"2021-02-14T12:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T12:15:38.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"66f087f33a6aab1a07ecec4b74e5d5c7f1b3a0b0","tid":2407894,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"今（14）日是一年一度的西洋情人節，在這個洋溢著溫暖與浪漫氣息的節日，許多名人搭上風潮，曝光了相關貼文，吸引粉絲關注。近幾年，堪稱是日本AV界霸主的三上悠亞，稍早就發文，曝光了情人節甜點塔，並秀出性感美胸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/14/3027041-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F14%2F3027041-PH.jpg&h=7ab76807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲三上悠亞情人節美圖。（圖／翻攝自@yua_mikami Twitter）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/14/3027042-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F14%2F3027042-PH.jpg&h=e3550e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從少女偶像轉戰AV界的三上，擁有極高知名度，粉絲遍及海內外，推特與IG都吸引超過百萬人追蹤。稍早，三上在推特發文，分享了呼應情人節的甜點塔並曝光美照。照片中，三上穿上白色與紅色相間的內衣，並巧妙透過拍攝方式與動作，展現出美胸溢出的視覺感，對鏡頭露出俏皮表情，舉手投足魅力十足。<br />\n<br />\n針對情人節，三上也說會在YouTube平台直播，與大家聊聊情人節的相關話題，美圖一出吸引近萬人按愛心，除了對美圖表達稱讚之外，多名網友也祝福女神情人節快樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/14/3027043-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F14%2F3027043-PH.jpg&h=22dbd1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲三上悠亞美圖。（圖／翻攝自@yua_mikami Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/19/2835557-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F19%2F2835557-PH.jpg&h=9f2b3514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/19/2835560-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F19%2F2835560-PH.jpg&h=c18ef267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce20b3083eefd4e983366cfd7912e2fad1f15d19","tid":2407894,"uid":53601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b9be5ff0a237dd758d53487a1faf0edbaeef0f","tid":2407894,"uid":7043,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"條女咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好似唔多出名既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cbd4495e4835361c92697a9063056847d1e090","tid":2407894,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b9be5ff0a237dd758d53487a1faf0edbaeef0f","tid":2407894,"uid":7043,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"條女咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好似唔多出名既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf28d768cbb1834fe76837af921ebba51e3d9e7","tid":2407894,"uid":261849,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"佢真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無吸引力"},{"pid":"b6c9e74f052012dc518bdb7730bddec59d58d65a","tid":2407894,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16b9be5ff0